text: József Hegedűs (7 January 1910 - 7 August 1981) was a Hungarian gymnast. He competed at the 1932 Summer Olympics and the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
